Let me explain something to you, EQ is a GAME.  It doesn't cure cancer.  It won't make your penis larger.  It won't get rid of the zits lining your face from the 18 chocolate bars you had last night so while playing for 38 hours straight.  EQ is just the latest fucking version of Pong.

I don't want every spell, just want to be able to enjoy a character that I have been playing for awhile.  Everyone plays EQ in their own way.  I have no problem with people who commit alot more effort into EQ getting more outta of it, I just want it to be viable for me to still play it in the way I choose.


Screech
